2020/7/28

正規分布

x <- seq(from=-2,to=2,length=101)
pdf <- dnorm(x)

y <- pnorm(x) - 0.5

X <- cbind(x,rep(1,length(x)))
Y <- cbind(y,rep(0,length(y)))
plot(rbind(X,Y))
for(i in 1:length(x)){
  segments(X[i,1],X[i,2],Y[i,1],Y[i,2])
}

plot(sort(y))

n <- 100
x <- rnorm(n)

y <- pnorm(x) - 0.5

X <- cbind(x,rep(1,length(x)))
Y <- cbind(y,rep(0,length(y)))
plot(rbind(X,Y))
for(i in 1:length(x)){
  segments(X[i,1],X[i,2],Y[i,1],Y[i,2])
}

plot(sort(y))
